data.description: Space, storage and coziness combine in this 4 bedroom brick ranch.  Upon entering you are greeted by a huge living room with wood floors and coat closet.  The kitchen features newer appliances and a cut out view into the dining room.  From the dining room you can enter the attached garage through one door and the wooden back deck in the flat fenced in backyard through another.  A unique feature of this home is the jack and jill full bath with a door that leads down a short hall into the kitchen at one end and a door into the largest of the main floor bedrooms at the other end.  Down the longer hall you find two more bedrooms as well as a linen closet and pantry closet.  The basement is full of possibilities.  The finished side has two large rooms with updated carpet.   The family room with its wood burning fire place leads into what can be the fourth bedroom, office, playroom, gym or suit a variety of needs.  The unfinished half also has two rooms.  The first a storage room with sump pump which leads to the laundry room.  The  current dryer is electric but there is hook up for gas which can also run  above into the kitchen for a gas range.  All of this in a location convenient to many stores, restaurants and other accommodations.  Schedule your appointment today!
